### Get User Profile
# This request fetches the user profile with the specified userId.
GET http://localhost:5000/api/UserProfile/{userId}
Content-Type: application/json

### Save User Profile
# This request saves a new user profile.
POST http://localhost:5000/api/UserProfile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user1",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "preferences": "{ \"theme\": \"dark\", \"notifications\": true }"
}

### Get Device Event History
# This request fetches the device event history for the specified deviceId.
GET http://localhost:5000/api/DeviceEventHistory/{deviceId}
Content-Type: application/json

### Save Device Event History
# This request saves a new device event history record.
POST http://localhost:5000/api/DeviceEventHistory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "event1",
  "deviceId": "device1",
  "temperature": 23.5,
  "humidity": 45.2,
  "timestamp": "2024-01-01T12:00:00Z"
}

